{"tid":2101542,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"［三叔跟機 ］網傳最快明年落實   Samsung 或停止跟機提供充電器","createTime":"2020-07-10T01:25:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-14T18:46:41.000Z","uid":105567,"like":1,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"5e36ff961fcbd4b6901648dfd61fa5d3245f5b20","tid":2101542,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T01:25:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2020/07/10/samsung-may-stop-providing-charger/mobile-phone/phone-parts/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2020%2F07%2F10%2Fsamsung-may-stop-providing-charger%2Fmobile-phone%2Fphone-parts%2F&d=gCjj53haX7oQ0UVj6qLsjjC6QH3F2wvzJ1VFJz7MVw4%3D&h=af7843cb\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2020/07/10/samsung-may-stop-providing-charger/mobile-phone/phone-parts/</a><br />\n<br />\n最近有不少 iPhone 12 不再跟機提供充電器和免提耳機的消息流出，根據韓國網站 ETNews 的報導，Samsung 亦有類似的打算，但就只會停止提供充電器，免提耳機可能會維持。報導指 Samsung 正在跟持份者進行討論，有關落實取消提供充電器的安排。"},{"pid":"a93aea142d6f628a096df15cab1952dc8a9957d3","tid":2101542,"uid":109923,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T01:32:17.000Z","msg":"我預言3年內an機都跟風唔附送耳機&amp;叉電器<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2086199\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2086199</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n三星考慮下年跟隨蘋果，隨機不會附送叉電器<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2100244\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2100244</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"513f2239081977ffe7a5cedf99b40d51ac3f804e","tid":2101542,"uid":1888,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T01:57:08.000Z","msg":"三叔狗屌完Apple<br />\n公平d屌埋自己老豆啦"},{"pid":"628af57bf2fa8fb87eb8f29497f47045b2906b5e","tid":2101542,"uid":70392,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"513f2239081977ffe7a5cedf99b40d51ac3f804e","tid":2101542,"uid":1888,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T01:57:08.000Z","msg":"三叔狗屌完Apple<br />\n公平d屌埋自己老豆啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T01:59